			<node ID="ID_136757767" TEXT="Variation of Parameters (that we will learn here) which works on a wide range of functions but is a little messy to use. Variation of Parameters To keep things simple we are only going to look at the case: d 2 ydx 2 + p dydx + qy = f(x) where p and q are constants and f(x) is a non-zero function of x." />
