			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1602956038" LINK="http://tutorial.math.lamar.edu/Classes/DE/HOVariationOfParam.aspx" TEXT="Differential Equations - Variation of Parameters">
			<node ID="ID_99652464" TEXT="Section 7-4 : Variation of Parameters. We now need to take a look at the second method of determining a particular solution to a differential equation. As we did when we first saw Variation of Parameters we&#8217;ll go through the whole process and derive up a set of formulas that can be used to generate a particular solution." />
