			<node ID="ID_1897587656" TEXT="When is the mode the best measure of central tendency? The mode is the least used of the measures of central tendency and can only be used when dealing with nominal data. For this reason the mode will be the best measure of central tendency (as it is the only one appropriate to use) when dealing with nominal data." />
