			<node ID="ID_332603358" TEXT="In probability theory and statistics a probability distribution is a mathematical function that provides the probabilities of occurrence of different possible outcomes in an experiment. In more technical terms the probability distribution is a description of a random phenomenon in terms of the probabilities of events." />
