		<node ID="ID_1728051023" LINK="https://www.sagepub.com/sites/default/files/upm-binaries/40007_Chapter8.pdf" TEXT="Introduction to Hypothesis Testing">
			<node ID="ID_455864971" TEXT="Hypothesis testing or significance testing is a method for testing a claim or hypothesis about a parameter in a population using data measured in a sample. In this method we test some hypothesis by determining the likelihood that a sample statistic could have been selected if the hypothesis regarding the population parameter were true." />
			</node>
