			<node ID="ID_961594001" TEXT="Hypothesis Testing Example. A common statistical method is to compare the means of various groups. For example you might have come up with a measurable hypothesis that children will gain a higher IQ if they eat oily fish for a period of time.. Your alternative hypothesis H 1 would be &#8220;Children who eat oily fish for six months show an increase in IQ when compared to children who have not." />
